# Kaizen Improvement Review
## Airlines Management System - Week 3

| What was Built | Problem/Limitation Found | Improvement Idea | Team Member Responsible | Expected Impact |
|----------------|--------------------------|------------------|-------------------------|-----------------|
| Flight Linked List | Manual traversal needed for search | Implement hash table for O(1) flight lookup | Solo Student | Reduce search time from O(n) to O(1) |
| Departure Queue | Queue displays all items when large | Add pagination (show next 10 departures) | Solo Student | Better user experience with large datasets |
| Client History Stack | No persistent storage | Save history to file on exit | Solo Student | Data persistence between program runs |
| Seat Management | No seat selection/assignment | Add seat map with row/column selection | Solo Student | Realistic airline booking system |
| Input Validation | No validation for time format | Add regex validation for HHMM format | Solo Student | Prevent incorrect data entry |
| Memory Management | Memory leaks on delete | Implement destructor to clean all nodes | Solo Student | Prevent memory leaks |
| User Interface | Text-only interface | Add color coding for different message types | Solo Student | Improved readability |
